These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, marigold, amaryllis
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, mexican, brazilian
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, go-climbing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, musical, satire
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess, go
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, mouse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is the indonesian##1
 3. the brazilian is the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the indonesian##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is go-climbing##2
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
13. the mexican is on the left of the person playing go##1
14. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
16. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
18. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
19. the person playing whist is the colombian##1
20. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
21. the person watching adventure movies is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Flower      | amaryllis        | marigold   | bellflower         | zinnia  |
| Nationality          | mexican         | indonesian   | colombian   | brazilian |
| Hobby         | go-climbing | puzzles    | video-games | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | adventure  | satire      | musical   |
| Game   | chess          | go       | whist        | canasta   |
| Pet           | rabbit        | mouse      | goldfish    | lizard    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | volleyball | rowing      | sailing   |

