.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, december, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, iris, bellflower
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, italian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, rabbit, turtle
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, chess, go
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, train, trike
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 3. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the bus is the italian##1
12. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
15. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
17. the malaysian is in an even position##4
18. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the trike##1
19. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left or far right##3
20. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
21. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta         | coffee     | tea        | mirinda  |
| Birthday          | december          | march     | february    | january   |
| Flower   | zinnia          | iris      | poppy      | bellflower   |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | malaysian  | dutch      | italian  |
| Pet           | mouse         | turtle     | lizard     | rabbit   |
| Game         | chess | go | bridge | domino |
| Transport     | trike         | helicopter | train      | bus      |

