.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice, countryade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, country, reggae, folk
House: cape-cod, cottage, colonial, gothic-revival
City: nizza, boston, miami, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, snowboarding, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, helicopter, snowmobile
 1. the fan of reggae is between the person traveling to nizza and the colonial house##2
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking countryade##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
12. the fan of country is the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
16. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
17. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is basketball##1
18. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
19. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | countryade   | almond-milk  | juice         |
| Music-Genre          | trance       | reggae    | folk     | country         |
| House         | cape-cod | cottage      | colonial      | gothic-revival  |
| City   | nizza    | liverpool   | boston   | miami     |
| Pet           | horse       | pony       | guinea-pig   | goldfish      |
| Sport         | basketball  | ice-hockey | snowboarding | weightlifting |
| Transport     | boat        | helicopter | snowmobile   | airplane      |

