.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-4::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, pineapple, potato, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, hiking, rock-climbing, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, martial-arts, romance, superhero
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, nigerian, spanish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, november, may
City: new-york, colone, miami, berlin
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 7. the person eating banana is on the right of the dutch##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the canadian##3
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
15. the canadian is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person traveling to miami##2
16. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
17. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | pineapple | banana        | watermelon  | potato     |
| Hobby         | hiking    | rock-climbing | board-games | traveling  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts  | romance     | disaster   |
