 2. the architect is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the dutch is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who growsbegonia is the pilot##1
 6. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person playing billiard is the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the canadian is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the doctor##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
15. the person who growsmarigold is between the colombian and the person drinking fanta##2
16. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
17. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
18. the dressmaker is on the far right##1

