 8. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing billiard is the bongani-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
11. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
