 6. the analyst is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the manager is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
10. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
11. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
12. the project-manager is in an odd position##4
13. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
14. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
15. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person eating mango##1
16. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growsrose##1
17. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
