.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, coral, brown, ivory
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cherry, peas, pineapple
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, singing, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, hip-hop, metal
City: liverpool, berlin, new-york, nizza
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, parkour, rugby, ivory-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, subway, taxi
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
10. the person who likes coral is the fan of d&b##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who likes ivory##1
12. the person who likes brown is between the person eating peas and the person who likes coral##2
13. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
14. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is singing##1
15. the person driving the scooter is between the person eating pineapple and the person traveling to nizza##2
16. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
18. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is ivory-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |     4      |
| Color      | ivory      | lavender      | brown   | coral     |
| Food          | asparagus  | peas     | pineapple  | cherry     |
| Hobby   | fishing    | photography   | hiking     | singing    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | metal    | gospel     | d&b        |
| City   | nizza     | liverpool | new-york    | berlin  |
| Sport         | ivory-polo | rugby    | basketball | parkour    |
| Transport     | subway     | scooter  | taxi       | snowmobile |

