4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, old-henry, bolivar
City: hannover, rome, miami, edinburgh
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, project-manager, software-developer, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, house, punk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, aconite, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
 2. the fan of punk is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 8. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the writer is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of disco##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of house##1
12. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1
13. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the software-developer and the person who growsaconite##2
14. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
16. the person driving the quad-bike is the person traveling to miami##1
17. the project-manager is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
