 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
10. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
11. the person eating potato is between the person who's sport is baseball and the fan of reggae##2
12. the person eating watermelon is between the person playing bridge and the person playing snooker##2
13. the person eating watermelon is between the person who growsiris and the person watching crime movies##2
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
15. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
16. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of trance##1
17. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
18. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
